{"tid":2170017,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–膀胱如何避免受到尿液致病細菌感染","createTime":"2020-08-23T03:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:37:32.000Z","uid":38861,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"91d542692a57722e4f3dff03036a59758696f88e","tid":2170017,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"因人而異，膀胱/尿袋 (Urinary Bladder)一般來說可以儲存300-500ml尿液。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmLOUvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmLOUvi.jpg&h=14d433bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尿液的其中一個功能，就是將體內的毒素或細菌排出，而膀胱經常有大量尿液儲存，為罪惡的蘊藏之所，體內的警署。<br />\n<br />\n想深一層，身體的細菌經由尿液聚首一堂，膀胱豈不是非常容易令受到感染?<br />\n<br />\n（致病的細菌及毒素亦可從糞便排出）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）尿調理素(Uromodulin/Tamm&ndash;Horsfall Protein)是尿液其中一種常見的主要蛋白，主要在腎臟管道生產。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQ7xBJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQ7xBJH.jpg&h=9954f24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n它被認定為有抵禦細菌感染的作用，但一直以來也沒有充分的證據得以證明。<br />\n<br />\n近日，有科學家利用最新的電子顯微鏡技術及各種實驗輔證（Ref1)，終於確立得到尿調理素抵禦細菌感染的功能。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）先簡單重溫一下細菌的外部結構，今次我們會特別著重提及Pili，它賦予細菌與外部接觸的能力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TKDxg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TKDxg6.jpg&h=ebc80d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMfy5Cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMfy5Cd.jpg&h=20c7929e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）左邊是文中的圖片，黃色箭嘴頭所指示的就是細菌的pili，它能夠與uromodulin建立非常穩定的連結；<br />\n箇中的連結需要糖份組織的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）Uromodulin在尿液的大量存在，將會強迫致病的大腸桿菌聚在一起，以免大腸桿菌能夠與膀胱內壁接觸及進行感染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wub6GaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwub6GaC.jpg&h=e91d5d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以壓倒性的數量，簡單將致病的大腸桿菌聚集及封鎖在一起，這種防禦機制相對地直接簡單。<br />\n至於Uromodulin能否與所有已知的致命細菌結合、會否有著其他的機制及功能，還需要進一步的調查。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=0c83d9ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"orange\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=48879893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科普資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/369/6506/1005?ijkey=e112b23dc73c7c7bd746a5711869e4bf44026346&amp;keytype2=tf_ipsecsha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F369%2F6506%2F1005%3Fijkey%3De112b23dc73c7c7bd746a5711869e4bf44026346%26keytype2%3Dtf_ipsecsha&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=7d46ace2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/369/6506/1005?ijkey=e112b23dc73c7c7bd746a5711869e4bf44026346&amp;keytype2=tf_ipsecsha</a>"},{"pid":"1cd8d4e408657d49a6d1a5c6c69bd99658eaee28"