/腎有事. <br />\n2. 尿道炎D大腸桿菌係屎忽到來. 女仔尿道比男仔短得多同無9曲13彎, D菌易入D, 所以女比男更常見有尿道炎<br />\n3. Tamm-Horsfall protein無咩研究. 我學個時都係話唔知有咩用. 不過你講既野合理. 而醫生都會叫成日有尿道炎既人多飲水, 用尿沖走D爬緊上來既菌"},{"pid":"b39b897d5c6afdc489cc776b620d555f3e4e1627","tid":2170017,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd09d957feb8bdd7e39f23d82fa5eb1ac2d9488","tid":2170017,"uid":345137,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"補充返先: <br />\n1. 尿正常係無菌. 驗到有菌即係尿道炎/腎有事. <br />\n2. 尿道炎D大腸桿菌係屎忽到來. 女仔尿道比男仔短得多同無9曲13彎, D菌易入D, 所以女比男更常見有尿道炎<br />\n3. Tamm-Horsfall protein無咩研究. 我學個時都係話唔知有咩用. 不過你講既野合理. 而醫生都會叫成日有尿道炎既人多飲水, 用尿沖走D爬緊上來既菌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"能夠令同尿液管道感染的大腸桿菌，統稱為UPEC，Uropathogenic E coli，為兩性尿道應染的主因。<br />\n<br />\n依個關於Tamm-Horssfall Protein的研究，喺前兩日Science文章發表，詳細可睇#1的Reference，所以正路你學嗰時應該未有確實證據證明佢哋的關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"dac596b60312730c35cfb6e66961e8fa470f7312","tid":2170017,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bb2f400378986164760cfc90338584a3d9a62b","tid":2170017,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc2d40a7912e9a33502043312f9c59b003e0f59","tid":2170017,"uid":58642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d3080348610abb00331e307e019e1a1638e1a","tid":2170017,"u